caterpillar-foot-to-floor-ride-on-for-toddlers,CAT Foot to Floor Ride-On for Toddlers,"

Description

Introduce your toddler to the world of construction with the Caterpillar Foot to Floor ride-on toy. Designed for children aged 1 to 3 years, this toy features a vivid yellow color and is built to resemble a Caterpillar machine. The ride-on includes engine sounds to provide a realistic playtime experience and has a convenient under-seat storage area for your child's toys. The sturdy PP tires and seat ensure durability and safety for little riders. This foot-powered ride-on encourages physical activity and is perfect for developing motor skills.
• Authentic Caterpillar Design: This foot-to-floor ride-on is designed to mimic a Caterpillar construction vehicle, making it an exciting toy for young children who love big machines.
• Engine Sound Feature: Adds to the realism with engine sounds that activate during play, enhancing the fun for kids aged 1 to 3 years.
• Convenient Seat Storage: A hidden storage compartment under the seat allows toddlers to carry their favorite toys along with them.
• Durable Construction: Made with high-quality PP tires and seat, this ride-on is built to withstand the rough and tumble of playtime.
• Bright and Attractive Color: The vibrant yellow color of the ride-on is eye-catching and adds to the authentic Caterpillar experience.
• Safe for Toddlers: The design is safety-focused, with no small parts and a sturdy build to support up to 55 lbs (25 kgs).

Introduce your little ones to the timeless charm of the Chevrolet 3100 with this vintage push car. Designed for toddlers aged 2 years and above, this foot-to-floor model is perfect for enhancing motor skills and encouraging active play. The kid-size steering wheel ensures easy maneuverability, while the horn and music controls add to the realistic driving experience. With under-seat storage, your child can take their favorite toys along for the ride. The car's four-wheel design and anti-overturning system provide stability and safety as they scoot around. Best of all, no batteries are needed for this eco-friendly playtime adventure.
• Classic Push Car Design: A foot-to-floor ride-on styled after the iconic Chevrolet 3100, ideal for toddlers to develop coordination and motor skills.
• Easy Maneuvering: Features a kid-sized steering wheel that allows for easy steering and control, perfect for children aged 18-36 months.
• Interactive Play Features: Equipped with a horn and music on the steering wheel to create engaging and realistic playtime experiences.
• Convenient Under-Seat Storage: A hidden compartment under the seat provides space for little ones to carry their toys or snacks while on the move.
• Safe and Sturdy: Includes an anti-overturning system at the bottom to ensure safety when children push and slide around.
• Smooth Ride: The four-wheel design ensures a smooth and stable ride for young adventurers.

Exciting Ride-On Truck

The Freddo Fire Truck ride-on lets kids play hero with its realistic design and interactive features. Suitable for ages 3-8, it comes with a leather seat, LED lights, MP3/AUX input, Bluetooth, and a built-in radio. The truck is equipped with emergency lights, a megaphone, a sprinkler, and a fire shovel, enhancing the rescue mission experience. Safety is assured with a 2.4G remote control and an emergency stop button.
• Authentic Fire Truck Design: A vibrant red, one-seater fire truck ride-on designed for children aged 3-8, complete with front and rear alarm lights and a fireman's megaphone.
• Engaging Sound Effects: Equipped with music, sounds, and a functioning sprinkler, this ride-on offers a fully immersive playtime experience.
• Safety Features: Comes with a seat belt and an emergency stop button on the remote control, ensuring the child's safety during use.
• Parental Remote Control: The 2.4G remote control allows parents to oversee the ride, with two speed modes ranging from 1.4 to 2.5 km/h.
• Interactive Accessories: Includes a fire shovel and storage space at the back of the truck for realistic role-play and convenience.
• Durable and Comfortable: Features EVA tires for a smooth ride and a leather seat for added comfort during long rescue missions.

36v-freddo-electric-dirt-bike-for-teens,Freddo 36V Electric Dirt Bike with Brushless Motor,"

Teen Joyride

Unleash the thrill of off-roading with the Freddo Electric Dirt Bike 36V, tailored for teens aged 14 and above. It boasts a robust brushless hub motor that delivers a max speed of 16MPH (25KMH) and carries a load of up to 80kgs with ease. Designed for performance and durability, it features stepless speed changes, air-filled rubber wheels for superior traction, and rear disc braking for reliable stopping power. With a key ignition start switch and a manual bell, this bike ensures a safe and exhilarating ride. Charge up for 8-12 hours and enjoy up to 50 minutes of adventure.
• Premium Leather Seat: Experience comfort with a high-quality leather seat, designed for a solo rider, ensuring a stylish and enjoyable ride.
• Durable Rubber Air Wheels: Tackle any terrain with confidence thanks to the robust rubber air wheels, providing stability and traction for a smooth dirt biking adventure.
• Stepless Speed Control: Enjoy a seamless riding experience with the stepless speed change, allowing you to accelerate smoothly to a maximum speed of 16 MPH (25 KM/H).
• Reliable Motor: Powered by a 36V 350W brushless hub motor, this bike offers efficient and quiet operation, perfect for both beginners and experienced riders.
• Disc Braking System: The rear disc braking ensures responsive stopping power, giving you control and safety during your rides.
• Designed for Teens and Adults: With a weight capacity of 176 lbs (80 kgs) and an age recommendation of 14+, this dirt bike is suitable for a wide range of enthusiasts.

DTI Direct provides lifetime customer service and a 6-month parts warranty on parts, excluding batteries, tires, and chargers.

jeep-rubicon-foot-to-floor-ride-on-for-toddlers,Jeep Rubicon Foot to Floor Ride-On for Toddlers,"

Description

Get your little one ready for adventure with the Jeep Rubicon Foot to Floor ride-on toy. Suitable for children aged 1 to 3 years, this ride-on is designed to inspire active play and imagination. It features realistic engine sounds and has a handy storage compartment under the seat for toys. The durable PP construction and wide tires provide stability for safe play indoors and outdoors. This ride-on is available in red, white, grey, and pink, making it the perfect gift for any young explorer.
• Rugged Jeep Design: A foot-to-floor model designed to resemble the iconic Jeep Rubicon, offering a realistic playtime experience for children aged 1-3 years.
• Interactive Sound Features: Includes engine sounds to mimic a real Jeep adventure, enhancing the ride-on experience for little explorers.
• Convenient Storage: Features seat storage for toys and snacks, perfect for toddlers on the go.
• Sturdy and Safe: Made with durable PP tires and seat, this ride-on is built to support up to 55 lbs (25 kgs) for safe and long-lasting fun.
• Available in Multiple Colors: Comes in red, white, grey, and pink, allowing kids to choose their favorite color for their mini off-road adventures.
<li>Easy for Kids to Use: No batteries or remote controls needed
column2: kids can propel the vehicle with their feet, encouraging physical activity and motor skills development.

lamborghini-3-in-1-kids-push-ride-on-toy-car,Lamborghini 3-in-1 Kids Push Ride On Toy Car,"

Description

Introducing the Lamborghini 3-in-1 Ride-On Toy, an official licensed product perfect for children aged 3 and above. With a maximum load capacity of 30KG, this ride-on toy is designed to inspire your child's imagination and encourage active play. It features a front light (powered by dry cells) and built-in music for an immersive experience. The toy includes a convenient storage bin, high-quality plastic wheels, and a comfortable plastic seat. Safety is enhanced with a car guardrail and a seat backrest, while the push bar with turning function adds to the ease of use. Ideal for both indoor and outdoor use, this ride-on toy is a fantastic way for kids to engage in physical activity and develop their motor skills.
• Luxurious Comfort: Equipped with a premium leather seat for a single rider, ensuring a comfortable and stylish experience.
• Dazzling LED Lights: Features front LED lights for an exciting ride, enhancing visibility and adding a touch of realism.
• Durable Tires: Constructed with high-quality EVA tires, providing a smooth ride and long-lasting durability.
• Interactive Features: Boasts built-in speakers and front lights powered by dry cells, offering an engaging ride with music and illumination.
• Versatile Storage: Includes a convenient storage bin, allowing kids to take their favorite toys along for the ride.
• Suitable for Toddlers: Ideal for children aged 3+, supporting a maximum weight of 66 lbs (30 kgs), with a push bar for easy steering by parents.

column2: >Discover fun and prestige with our Lamborghini Swing Car for Kids! Ideal for youngsters aged 3 and up, this 1-seater captures the Lamborghini allure in a fun, leisurely swing. Authentic PU Flashing Tires and a TPE Tire add a touch of class, while its bright headlights and horn ramp up the fun. Crafted for comfort, safety, and style, this car ensures a snug and secure ride for your little one. Enjoy onboard melodies and store tiny treasures under the seat. It's not just a ride—it's a luxurious experience!

Go Seater: This 1-seater car promises a smooth journey with the added dazzle of headlights and the fun beep of a horn. Ergonomically crafted with adjustable footrests, its lightweight yet durable steel frame makes it the go-to for toddlers.

column1: Ready to Grow: Perfectly built for little ones aged 3 and up, it supports a weight limit of up to 66lbs, ensuring they can enjoy the ride for years to come.
Twinkle Tires: Let them roll in style with PU flashing tires and a TPE tire that lights up with every twist and turn, adding safety and fun to each ride.
Hidden Treasures Nook: The under-seat compartment is their little secret stash for snacks and toys, keeping their adventures organized.
Melody Magic: With a press, the music control unleashes delightful tunes and sound effects, adding that special sprinkle of fun to their cruises.

mercedes-antos-kids-foot-to-floor-ride-on,Mercedes Antos Kids' Foot to Floor Ride-On,"

Description

The Mercedes Antos Foot to Floor ride-on provides toddlers aged 1 to 3 years with a fun and engaging playtime experience. This red ride-on mimics a fire truck and is crafted with durable PP materials to withstand enthusiastic play. It features an interactive design with engine sounds that ignite a child's imagination, along with a convenient under-seat storage space for their toys. The ride-on is also equipped with lights for an added element of excitement. With its foot-to-floor design, it promotes physical activity and motor skill development.
• Foot-to-Floor Fun: Designed for toddlers aged 1-3 years, this ride-on Mercedes Antos encourages active play and mobility.
• Interactive Features: Includes an engine sound feature to create an immersive experience for little ones as they play.
• Convenient Storage: The ride-on comes with under-seat storage, allowing kids to take their favorite toys along for the ride.
• Built for Safety: With a sturdy PP construction and a design free from small parts, it's safe for toddlers to use.
• Stylish Design: The classic red color and Mercedes styling make it an attractive toy for any child.
<li>Easy to Use: No batteries or remote control needed
column2: kids can power the ride-on with their feet, developing strength and coordination.

24v-4x4-freddo-raptor-2-seater-ride-on-atv,24V 4x4 Freddo Raptor 2 Seater Ride on ATV,"

Description

Introducing the 24V 4x4 Freddo 2 Seater Ride on ATV for Kids - the perfect combination of style, safety, and excitement. Designed for kids aged 3-8 years old, this ride-on ATV can support a maximum weight of 130 lbs, making it suitable for a wide range of ages and sizes. Featuring EVA tires that provide excellent traction and stability on a variety of surfaces, this ATV is equipped with sturdy PP seats that are both comfortable and durable. LED lights add a touch of flare and provide added visibility, making it easier for your child to ride safely. To make the ride even more enjoyable, this ATV comes with Bluetooth, USB, and Aux connectivity options, allowing your child to listen to their favorite music.

• PP Seats: The ATV's seats are made from high-quality PP material, ensuring comfort and durability. The seats are designed to provide enough support for younger riders, and they are also easy to clean and maintain, ensuring a long-lasting product.

• LED Lights: This ATV is equipped with mounted LED lights that keep your kids safe and visible on rides, day or night. The LED lights are bright and easily visible, ensuring that other riders and pedestrians can see your kids, making it easier to ride with peace of mind.

• EVA Tires: This ATV is equipped with EVA tires that ensure a smooth and stable ride on different terrains. Whether your kids are riding on grass, gravel, or pavement, the EVA tires provide enough traction and stability to keep them safe and comfortable.

• Bluetooth + USB + Aux: This ATV comes with Bluetooth, USB, and Aux connectivity options, allowing your child to listen to their favorite music or audio books while exploring the outdoors on their ATV. Your kids can listen to their favorite songs, audiobooks, or even connect their phones or tablets to the ATV and enjoy a fun and adventurous ride.

• Battery: 24V 7AH: This ATV is powered by a powerful 24V 7AH battery, providing enough power for a long-lasting and fun ride. It can last up to several hours of continuous use, depending on the terrain and speed.

• Max Weight: 130 lbs: This ATV can carry a maximum weight of 130 pounds, making it perfect for two kids to ride together. Its weight capacity is designed to accommodate two average-sized children and still provide a safe and comfortable ride.

cascade-all-around-sup-kayak,Cascade All-Around SUP-Kayak,"

With the new CASCADE, adventures in nature will be easy but fascinating, combining kayaking and stand up paddle boarding fun into one. At 35” in width, this SUP kayak hybrid is very stable and the 8” thickness permits maximized volume that caters to family paddlers and those carrying great gear for long-distance adventures. The unique cockpit design, coming with our signature kayak spray skirt, allows it to be easily switched from a sit-on-top kayak to a sit-inside one for high speed kayaking. The full deck of deep-grooved EVA footpad ensures a non-slip and comfortable experience during stand up paddling. Constructed of Drop Stitch Light Technology, CASCADE is of great portability whilst being incredibly stiff. This valuable multi-functional kayak comes with a full accessories pack including directional twin fin system, double cargo nets and a premium padded high-back seat.
• CONSTRUCTION Double-chamber construction tactically designed for SUP-Kayak switch, creating a standing tray and a cockpit

Exciting Ride-On Truck

The Freddo Fire Truck ride-on lets kids play hero with its realistic design and interactive features. The truck is equipped with emergency lights, a megaphone, a sprinkler, and a fire shovel, enhancing the rescue mission experience. Safety is assured with a 2.4G remote control and an emergency stop button.

• Parental Remote Control: The 2.4G remote control allows parents to oversee the ride, with two speed modes ranging from 1.4 to 2.5 km/h.
• Interactive Accessories: Includes a fire shovel and storage space at the back of the truck for realistic role-play and convenience.
• Durable and Comfortable: Features EVA tires for a smooth ride and a leather seat for added comfort during long rescue missions.

Teen Joyride

Unleash the thrill of off-roading with the Freddo Electric Dirt Bike 36V, tailored for teens aged 14 and above. It boasts a robust brushless hub motor that delivers a max speed of 16MPH (25KMH) and carries a load of up to 80kgs with ease. Designed for performance and durability, it features stepless speed changes, air-filled rubber wheels for superior traction, and rear disc braking for reliable stopping power. With a key ignition start switch and a manual bell, this bike ensures a safe and exhilarating ride. Charge up for 8-12 hours and enjoy up to 50 minutes of adventure.
• Premium Leather Seat: Experience comfort with a high-quality leather seat, designed for a solo rider, ensuring a stylish and enjoyable ride.
• Durable Rubber Air Wheels: Tackle any terrain with confidence thanks to the robust rubber air wheels, providing stability and traction for a smooth dirt biking adventure.
• Stepless Speed Control: Enjoy a seamless riding experience with the stepless speed change, allowing you to accelerate smoothly to a maximum speed of 16 MPH (25 KM/H).
• Reliable Motor: Powered by a 36V 350W brushless hub motor, this bike offers efficient and quiet operation, perfect for both beginners and experienced riders.
• Disc Braking System: The rear disc braking ensures responsive stopping power, giving you control and safety during your rides.
• Designed for Teens and Adults: With a weight capacity of 176 lbs (80 kgs) and an age recommendation of 14+, this dirt bike is suitable for a wide range of enthusiasts.

column2: >Discover fun and prestige with our Lamborghini Swing Car for Kids! Ideal for youngsters aged 3 and up, this 1-seater captures the Lamborghini allure in a fun, leisurely swing. Authentic PU Flashing Tires and a TPE Tire add a touch of class, while its bright headlights and horn ramp up the fun. Crafted for comfort, safety, and style, this car ensures a snug and secure ride for your little one. Enjoy onboard melodies and store tiny treasures under the seat. It's not just a ride—it's a luxurious experience!

Go Seater: This 1-seater car promises a smooth journey with the added dazzle of headlights and the fun beep of a horn. Ergonomically crafted with adjustable footrests, its lightweight yet durable steel frame makes it the go-to for toddlers.

column1: Ready to Grow: Perfectly built for little ones aged 3 and up, it supports a weight limit of up to 66lbs, ensuring they can enjoy the ride for years to come.
Twinkle Tires: Let them roll in style with PU flashing tires and a TPE tire that lights up with every twist and turn, adding safety and fun to each ride.
Hidden Treasures Nook: The under-seat compartment is their little secret stash for snacks and toys, keeping their adventures organized.
Melody Magic: With a press, the music control unleashes delightful tunes and sound effects, adding that special sprinkle of fun to their cruises.
